        only affects the depth-arrangement of the screen.@{b}

    INPUTS@{ub}
        None@{b}

    RESULT@{ub}
        If the Workbench screen was opened, this function returns @{"TRUE" LINK "gg:doc/NDK/Guide/Include/exec/types.h/File" 95},
        otherwise it returns @{"FALSE" LINK "gg:doc/NDK/Guide/Include/exec/types.h/File" 98}.@{b}

    BUGS@{ub}@{b}

